* indiabridge.pkg -- net-install manifest
v 3

d indiabridge: fuzzy assignment of stable india-bridge state & district ids
d
d {cmd:indiabridge} reconciles messy Indian state and district names against the
d india-bridge dictionary by round-aware fuzzy string matching (matchit, n-gram
d similarity) and returns stable, time-consistent identifiers (Census 1951-2011
d and the Local Government Directory).
d
d Requires {cmd:matchit} (J. Raffo) and {cmd:strkeep} (R. Chu); both install from
d SSC automatically on first run if missing.
d
d Distribution-Date: 20260615
d Vedarshi Shastry, vedshastry.com

* program files
f indiabridge.ado
f indiabridge.sthlp

* dictionaries read at runtime (relative to the installed ado)
f dict/state_names.csv
f dict/dist_names.csv
f dict/id_st_indiabridge.csv
f dict/id_dt_indiabridge.csv
f dict/state/st_crosswalk.csv
f dict/state/st_lgd.csv
f dict/state/st_year_dict.csv
f dict/district/dt_crosswalk.csv
f dict/district/dt_year_dict.csv
